DTField.Name: PICKLIST
DTField.Label: PICKLIST
DTField.DTFieldHelp: Pick list identifier.

DTField.Name: PICKTYPE
DTField.Label: PICKTYPE
DTField.DTFieldHelp: Determines whether inventory will be picked by Load (e.g. fullpick) or from a Load (e.g. partial).

DTField.Name: PICKMETHOD
DTField.Label: PICKMETHOD
DTField.DTFieldHelp: Determines the method according to which the system will plan the picking of waves (e.g. Batch Pick, Parallel Pick, Pick by Customer, Pick by Item, Pick by Order, Pick by Rout, Pick by Truck, Single Pick).

DTField.Name: STRATEGYID
DTField.Label: STRATEGYID
DTField.DTFieldHelp: The Picking Policy used to when performing the Pick List picking Tasks.

DTField.Name: CREATEDATE
DTField.Label: CREATEDATE
DTField.DTFieldHelp: Pick List creation date.

DTField.Name: PLANDATE
DTField.Label: PLANDATE
DTField.DTFieldHelp: The date on which the pick list was planned.

DTField.Name: RELEASEDATE
DTField.Label: RELEASEDATE
DTField.DTFieldHelp: The date on which the pick list was released.

DTField.Name: ASSIGNEDDATE
DTField.Label: ASSIGNEDDATE
DTField.DTFieldHelp: The date on which the pick list was assigned to a user.

DTField.Name: COMPLETEDDATE
DTField.Label: COMPLETEDDATE
DTField.DTFieldHelp: The date on which the pick list was completed

DTField.Name: STATUS
DTField.Label: STATUS
DTField.DTFieldHelp: Refers to the entire Pick List and is determined according to functions performed on the Pick List.

DTField.Name: WAVE
DTField.Label: WAVE
DTField.DTFieldHelp: The Wave according to which the Pick List was created.

DTField.Name: HANDELINGUNITTYPE
DTField.Label: HANDELINGUNITTYPE
DTField.DTFieldHelp: The handeling unit type that is used for picking.

DTField.Name: ADDDATE
DTField.Label: ADDDATE
DTField.DTFieldHelp: The date on which data was added.

DTField.Name: ADDUSER
DTField.Label: ADDUSER
DTField.DTFieldHelp: The user who added the data.

DTField.Name: PICKLISTLINE
DTField.Label: PICKLISTLINE
DTField.DTFieldHelp: Pick list line identifier.

DTField.Name: PICKREGION
DTField.Label: PICKREGION
DTField.DTFieldHelp: The pick region from which inventory is allocated to the pick list.

DTField.Name: CONSIGNEE
DTField.Label: CONSIGNEE
DTField.DTFieldHelp: The Client for which the Pick List was created.

DTField.Name: USERID
DTField.Label: USERID
DTField.DTFieldHelp: The Outbound Order ID that was planned for to create the Pick List.

DTField.Name: ORDERLINE
DTField.Label: ORDERLINE
DTField.DTFieldHelp: The Outbound Order Line that was planned for to create Pick List lines.

DTField.Name: SKU
DTField.Label: SKU
DTField.DTFieldHelp: The SKU to be picked.

DTField.Name: priority
DTField.Label: priority
DTField.DTFieldHelp: The priority of orders allocated to the pick list.
